
  <sn><md>### Evolution of Civilization

**Culture and Civilization:** Culture refers to the `way of life` of the people of a society. Through continuous efforts, human life gradually progresses and improves. New discoveries are made in science and technology. 

&gt; This advanced stage or `form of culture` is called civilization.

The use of `fire and tools` marked the beginning of civilization. The earliest civilizations emerged in the continents of `Asia and Africa`. The fertile valleys of several major rivers served as the cradles of ancient civilizations.
</md></sn>
